                "description": {
                    "value": "<p><strong>Frequency</strong> once per round</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Effect</strong> The melomach's footsteps raise a clanging sound through their body to create a brief musical phrase. The melomach Strides, then generates the effect of one of the following bard composition cantrips at 7th rank: @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Allegro], @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Dirge of Doom] (adds the fear trait), or @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Triple Time].</p>"
