            "img": "systems/pf2e/icons/default-icons/action.svg",
            "name": "Scream",
            "sort": 600000,
            "system": {
                "actionType": {
                    "value": "action"
                },
                "actions": {
                    "value": 2
                },
                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>The melomach unleashes a guttural, ear-piercing wail. All creatures in a @Template[type:cone|distance:120] take @Damage[7d12[sonic]] damage with a @Check[type:fortitude|dc:32] save.</p>\n<p>The melomach can't Scream again for [[/br 1d4 #Recharge Scream]]{1d4 rounds}.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Critical Success</strong> The creature is unaffected.</p>\n<p><strong>Success</strong> The creature takes half damage.</p>\n<p><strong>Failure</strong> The creature takes full damage, is @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Stunned]{Stunned 1}, and is @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Deafened] for 1 minute.</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> The creature takes double damage, is @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Stunned]{Stunned 3}, and is deafened permanently.</p>"
                },
